name: Speedy Kiwi
description:
GO FULL SCREEN

Made by connercrab

You are a KIWI

You like ACORNS

You Are SPEEDY!

You can play through 9 action packed levels (sort of). See how fast you can gather all the acorns within the time limit. Hone your skills to improve your time.

Taste that sweet victory!

This is my first ever project.

Using Unity and some tutorials for reference, I tried to make as many of the assets myself as possible.
